data.description: Completely remodeled condo just one mile from I-25 and Hampden. Enjoy care-free living as this elevated first-floor condo was just rebuilt from the studs out (plumbing, electric, heating, updated kitchen/baths, etc.) and has a nearly all-inclusive HOA (water, heat, trash, insurance, fitness center, indoor/outdoor pools, hot tub, saunas, steam rooms, clubhouse, snow removal, etc.). Updated kitchen with brand new appliances, under-cabinet lighting and pantry. Private, in-unit laundry room with large-load washer and dryer. Master suite includes huge, walk-in closet and brand new 3/4 bath. New, in-wall AC in both bedrooms and living area. Elevator access from attached, community garage. New carpet, doors, paint, blinds . . . the list goes on. Secure/safe building in a highly popular and convenient part of town - in-between Downtown and Tech Center. Walk or drive to grocery stores (K. Soopers/Whole Foods/Target), theaters, restaurants, parks, bars, etc. I-25 and light rail within one mile.
